text: Taeniesthes specularis is a species of scarab beetle.BiolibGlobal Names Global NamesBold Systems ==Description== Taeniesthes specularis can reach a length of about .Le monde des insectes These medium-sized beetles have a black pronotum with brownish red edges. Elytra are black, with broad, brownish yellow stripes on each side. ==Distribution== This species is widespread in Kenya and Tanzania.
